The '''Corellian Slip''' was a type of [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Starfighter combat/Legends|combat]] maneuver. When an enemy fighter trailed a friendly craft, another friendly ship would fly directly at both friend and foe, veering off at the last moment to destroy the attacking enemy ship. The tactic was named after the [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] who supposedly invented it.

During the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] performed a Corellian Slip to shoot down [[DS-61-4]], who was chasing [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]].

